That sounds good. It's been a 
while since we had a meeting.

312
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:30,040
Will Dr. Kano be back by then?

313
00:34:30,200 --> 00:34:32,920
Of course he will!

314
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,880
Wait a minute...

315
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:37,360
