right? I wonder why he took her.

325
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:06,280
She's not been the same since.

326
00:36:06,520 --> 00:36:08,760
She's lost all of her spark.

327
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:11,520
- Big disappointment for me, too.
- Come, now.

328
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:13,720
Talk about that topic is 
out of bounds for today!

329
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:19,800
Time to eat.

330
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:23,920
- Dr. Kano - have you seen Sadako?
- No.

331
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:26,600
- Have you seen Sadako?
- She headed off that way earlier.

332
00:36:26,720 --> 00:36:28,600
I wonder where she's got to.

333
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:32,560
Let's go eat.

334
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:59,840
Where's the other half?

335
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:27,160
And just who might you be?

336
00:37:30,560 --> 00:37:32,080
Kosuke Kindaichi.

337
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:34,960
The private detective?

338
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:38,560
What gives you the 
right to be here?

339
