I paid 5000 yen to become 
a registered participant.

340
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:45,240
Seems it was all 
for nought, however.

341
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,520
You knew this was 
going to happen?

342
00:37:48,560 --> 00:37:51,760
Don't be ridiculous - if I did, 
I would've done something.

343
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:56,360
I'd like you all to 
return to the hotel.

344
