What time did you last 
meet with Sadako, Doctor?

359
00:39:40,200 --> 00:39:43,200
One o'clock, perhaps? 
I'm afraid I don't recall.

360
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:45,720
I understand. An approximate 
time will do fine.

361
