Why are you treating 
us like criminals?

362
00:39:49,160 --> 00:39:51,840
We're merely asking 
everyone the same questions...

363
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:54,560
- The murder weapon has been found.
- Has it?

364
00:40:05,240 --> 00:40:08,520
