- Dr. Kano?

365
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:15,240
Bellboy!

366
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:17,720
Do you remember 
seeing that suitcase?

367
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:19,080
Yes, sir.

368
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:23,760
Someone who was referred by 
Dr. Kano was carrying it last night.

369
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:27,960
You, manager - wasn't 
the place fully reserved?

370
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:32,000
I received a call from Dr. Kano 
asking if he could arrive early.

371
00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:35,440
