quality if it's just a mannequin?

400
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:09,720
I wonder what it's being used for.

401
00:43:10,520 --> 00:43:13,720
Beats me -

402
00:43:13,960 --> 00:43:18,560
the guy said it just needed 
to show up well in a photo.

403
00:43:18,680 --> 00:43:20,720
Nothing unusual.

404
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:23,440
What kind of person 
made the order?

405
00:43:24,200 --> 00:43:26,520
Someone just like you.

406
